In the MATTER OF Christopher J. BUCKLEY, an Attorney at Law (Attorney No. 000082010) D-108 Sept. Term 2018
082681 Supreme Court of New Jersey. March 29, 2019

ORDER

This matter having been duly presented, it is ORDERED that Christopher J. Buckley of Jersey City, who was admitted to the bar of this State in 2010, and who was suspended from the practice of law for a period of three months effective October 21, 2016 by Order of this Court filed September 20, 2016, be restored to the practice of law, effective immediately.
